1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:02,500
I hated my father

2
00:00:02,500 --> 00:00:04,500
for twenty years

3
00:00:04,500 --> 00:00:07,000
for his silence,

4
00:00:07,000 --> 00:00:10,500
until I opened his closet.

5
00:00:10,500 --> 00:00:13,000
He never replied

6
00:00:13,000 --> 00:00:16,000
to my childhood letters.

7
00:00:16,000 --> 00:00:18,500
I assumed he chose

8
00:00:18,500 --> 00:00:21,000
a life without me.

9
00:00:21,000 --> 00:00:24,000
I found a dusty shoebox

10
00:00:24,000 --> 00:00:27,000
tucked behind his coats.

11
00:00:27,000 --> 00:00:30,000
Inside were my letters,

12
00:00:30,000 --> 00:00:33,000
and his unmailed replies.

13
00:00:33,000 --> 00:00:35,500
His letters revealed

14
00:00:35,500 --> 00:00:38,500
my mother’s criminal past,

15
00:00:38,500 --> 00:00:41,500
and his terrifying need

16
00:00:41,500 --> 00:00:44,000
to keep me hidden.

17
00:00:44,000 --> 00:00:47,000
He sacrificed our relationship

18
00:00:47,000 --> 00:00:48,500
to keep me alive.